    <string name="welcome_title_1">Welcome to FastMediaSorter!</string>
    <string name="welcome_description_1">FastMediaSorter is a powerful tool for organizing your media files.\n\n‚Ä¢ Browse photos, videos, GIFs, and audio files\n‚Ä¢ Sort and filter by name, date, or size\n‚Ä¢ Copy or move files with simple gestures\n‚Ä¢ Support for local folders, network shares (SMB), and SFTP\n‚Ä¢ Set up to 10 quick destination folders\n‚Ä¢ Slideshow mode for media playback\n\nLet\'s get started with a quick tour!</string>
    <string name="welcome_title_2">Resource Types</string>
    <string name="welcome_description_2">FastMediaSorter supports multiple resource types for flexible media management:\n\nüì± LOCAL RESOURCES:\n‚Ä¢ Device internal storage\n‚Ä¢ SD cards and external storage\n‚Ä¢ Camera and Downloads folders\n\nüåê NETWORK RESOURCES:\n‚Ä¢ SMB/CIFS network shares (Windows/NAS)\n‚Ä¢ SFTP servers (SSH file transfer)\n‚Ä¢ WebDAV protocol support\n\n‚òÅÔ∏è CLOUD STORAGE (Coming soon):\n‚Ä¢ Google Drive\n‚Ä¢ OneDrive\n‚Ä¢ Dropbox\n\nYou can add and manage resources in Settings!</string>
    <string name="welcome_title_3">Touch Zones (Images/Video)</string>
    <string name="welcome_description_3" formatted="false">Navigate and manage media with 9 touch zones (3x3 grid):\n\nTOP ROW:\n‚Ä¢ BACK - exit player\n‚Ä¢ COPY - copy file to destination\n‚Ä¢ RENAME - rename current file\n\nMIDDLE ROW:\n‚Ä¢ PREVIOUS - previous file\n‚Ä¢ MOVE - move file to destination\n‚Ä¢ NEXT - next file\n\nBOTTOM ROW (75% of screen):\n‚Ä¢ COMMAND PANEL - show quick actions\n‚Ä¢ DELETE - remove file\n‚Ä¢ SLIDESHOW - toggle auto-play mode\n\nNote: Bottom 25% is reserved for video controls.</string>
    <string name="welcome_title_4">Resources and Destinations</string>
    <string name="welcome_description_4">Organize your media workflow efficiently:\n\nRESOURCES (Source Folders):\n‚Ä¢ Add local device folders (Camera, Downloads, etc.)\n‚Ä¢ Connect to network shares via SMB/CIFS\n‚Ä¢ Access SFTP servers\n‚Ä¢ Each resource shows media file count and types\n\nDESTINATIONS (Quick Copy/Move):\n‚Ä¢ Configure up to 10 destination folders\n‚Ä¢ Assign colors to each destination\n‚Ä¢ Quick access via gestures or buttons\n‚Ä¢ Support both local and network locations\n\nYou can configure everything in Settings later!</string>
    
